  "report_text": "# Model Gateway and Routing Layer\n\nPublic gateway documentation and repositories make provider routing and abstraction visible as a separate operational layer in AI infrastructure.[1][2]\n\nThe same public materials are less definitive about how much adjacent control-plane scope belongs inside that layer, so comparisons should keep the core routing claim separate from the more tentative claim about policy and observability ownership.[1][2]\n",
